p1.name: Rex
p1.quote: The war left its scars on all of us

p2.name: Cody
p2.quote: This new Empire.. Are we making the galaxy better?

p3.name: Hunter
p3.quote: Blind allegiance makes you a pawn. A real leader protects his squad.

p4.name: Jesse
p4.quote: Commander Rex, you are in violation of Order 66. I accuse you of treason against the Grand Army of the Republic. You'll be demoted of rank Commander and subject to execution alongside the traitor, Ahsoka Tano.

p5.name: Echo
p5.quote: Its ironic. Clones wanted names instead of numbers, yet now people are signing up to be given numbers.

p6.name: Fives
p6.quote: He has a name. No clone uses their number. Not anymore.

p7.name: Kix
p7.quote: A good droid is a dead one

p9.name: Tech
p9.quote: There is no time, Wrecker. Plan 99

p10.name: Crosshair
p10.quote: We're soldiers. We do what needs to be done.
